<h2>Account Suspended</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>Important Notice:</strong> Your OMS Platform Administrator account has been suspended.</p>
</div>

<p>Your account access has been temporarily suspended for the following reason:</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p><strong>Suspension Details:</strong></p>
  <p>Reason: {{reason}}<br>
  Suspended By: {{suspendedBy}}<br>
  Date: {{suspensionDate}}</p>
</div>

{{#if isTemporary}}
<p>This is a temporary suspension. Your access will be restored on {{reactivationDate}}.</p>
{{else}}
<p>This suspension requires review. Please contact the platform administrator for more information.</p>
{{/if}}

<p>During this time, you will not be able to:</p>
<ul style="color: #4a5568; margin-left: 20px;">
  <li>Access the platform administration panel</li>
  <li>Manage users or tenants</li>
  <li>View system analytics</li>
  <li>Perform any administrative actions</li>
</ul>

<div class="divider"></div>

<p>If you believe this suspension was made in error or have questions, please contact:</p>
<p><strong>Platform Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:itsupport@omsystem.com">itsupport@omsystem.com</a></p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>OMS Platform Team</strong></p>
